---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Breadcrumbs from "../components/Breadcrumbs.astro";
import { SITE, authors } from "../lib/blog-data.js";
---

<BaseLayout
  title={`About - ${SITE.name}`}
  description={`关于${SITE.name}：${SITE.description}。`}
  canonical="/about"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 py-12">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[{ label: "Home", to: "/" }, { label: "About" }]} />

    <header class="mt-6">
      <div class="meta-label text-primary">About</div>
      <h1 class="mt-2 font-serif text-5xl font-semibold leading-[1.05]">
        一个可以自言自语的自留地。
      </h1>
    </header>

    <div class="prose-article mt-10">
      <p>
        {SITE.name}是{SITE.description}。这里没什么正经的规划，就是随手记记、自言自语，写点无关痛痒的东西。
      </p>
      <p>
        不追热点，不赶进度，想写就写，写完就搁着。你要是路过看到了，随便翻翻就好。
      </p>
      <h2 id="what-we-publish">写些什么</h2>
      <p>
        大多是些琐碎的念头和随笔，暂时还没定下来。内容会慢慢长出来，站主之后再补。
      </p>
      <h2 id="who-we-are">关于站主</h2>
      <p>肉骨明。在这块自留地上随手写写，无关痛痒。</p>
    </div>

    <section class="mt-12 border-t border-border pt-10">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold">Contributors</h2>
      <div class="mt-6 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        {
          authors.map((author) => (
            <a href={`/authors/${author.slug}`} class="group flex items-start gap-3">
              <img src={author.avatar} alt="" width="48" height="48" class="h-12 w-12 rounded-full" />
              <div>
                <div class="font-serif text-base font-semibold group-hover:text-primary">{author.name}</div>
                <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground">{author.bio}</div>
              </div>
            </a>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
